high_descs: Turn around and stand to the right of the stove.
Pick up the ladle next to the coffee maker.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Rinse the ladle in the sink.
Move to the left and face the toaster.
Put the ladle on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed ladle on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen island, then turn left and walk up to the part of counter top to the right of the oven.
Pick up the large golden spoon with a blue handle.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the large golden spoon with a blue handle into the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk over to where the toaster is on the counter.
Put down the large golden spoon with a blue handle on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean golden spoon on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the kitchen stove and face the counter
Pick up the spatula off of the counter
Turn around and walk towards the sink and face it
Place spatula in the sink and clean off with water, followed by picking back up
Turn toward the left and face the counter in front of the toaster
Place the spatula on the counter in front of the toaster
Turn around and go to the left to find the stove at the back of the kitchen.
Pick up the laddle off the corner of the counter, to the right of the stove.
Turn right a few steps to find the sink.
Put the laddle in the sink and turn the water on, then off again. Take the laddle out of the sink.
Take a few steps left to find the toaster on the counter.
Place the laddle on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Wash a laddle and place it on the counter.
